{"tid":2493560,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚印 特汁燒烤雞柳","createTime":"2021-04-18T04:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T13:03:27.000Z","uid":33359,"like":46,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9424e0a57e7f069d6808e4fa6d185a1e17ad24","tid":2493560,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFu6zd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFu6zd7.jpg&h=500d6560&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7RyZUea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RyZUea.jpg&h=8409cf91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zrdeef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zrdeef.jpg&h=806f7651&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sz1HR0Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSz1HR0Y.jpg&h=b4c1bcb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都知九龍城既秦國菜好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以今日就專登黎九龍城食印度菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為唔知會跟餐有烤餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我另外再叫咗份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢份又同跟餐個隻唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n薄脆啲 跟個薄荷醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n薄荷醬入口清新微酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但之後開始愈黎愈辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辣得幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特汁食到好香濃既茄味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食得出落咗好多新鮮番茄落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又唔似茄汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似係有茄香茄酸又少啲咖哩味既咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞柳非常嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嫩到似雞髀肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有炭燒香氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟餐個餅熱食個陣好軟熟好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但食到最尾個塊凍咗就有啲un<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個餐食落個印度好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ffc9750206ccf42612e97dc06aed689259056f","tid":2493560,"uid":90791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"九龍城?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11ef94f331782255b442467e45895b1979c5918","tid":2493560,"uid":34394,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"正過番印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce335434d45b6f0c265d5bd3b67e767951de456","tid":2493560,"uid":234527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"4b9932c356acc9225fb9b078dd8a867c6c5e74f7","tid":2493560,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"唔係你跳樓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d66f8341ed85e0ffe00484d6497990648c48b0b","tid":2493560,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:09:53.000Z","msg":"幾塊餅夠飽？"},{"pid":"6cc066a43f917688377bf598b64bd79ecf688af3","tid":2493560,"uid":369075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"終於食家鄉菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207998ff048a68e7ede2c80687b4985bd67b75ff","tid":2493560,"uid":39224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1